title: Benaẓīr Bhuṭṭo vilādat se shahādat tak

description.value: On the life and assassination of Benazir Bhutto,ex-prime minister and leader of Pakistan People's Party on December 27, 2007 in Rawalpindi, Pakistan.

notes.value:
"Qurbāniyon̲, jurāton̲, ḥauṣalon̲ aur jumhūrī jahd-i musalsal kī bemis̲āl dāstān".
